Record Class AssembleConfig

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
ca.gc.cra.radar.config.AssembleConfig
Record Components:
ioMode - input mode (IoMode.FILE or IoMode.KAFKA)
kafkaBootstrap - Kafka bootstrap servers when Kafka is used
kafkaSegmentsTopic - topic supplying captured segments in Kafka mode
kafkaHttpPairsTopic - topic receiving HTTP pairs in Kafka mode
kafkaTnPairsTopic - topic receiving TN3270 pairs in Kafka mode
inputDirectory - directory containing serialized segment files when in file mode
outputDirectory - root directory for assembled outputs
httpEnabled - whether HTTP reconstruction is enabled
tnEnabled - whether TN3270 reconstruction is enabled
httpOutputDirectory - optional override for HTTP output directory
tnOutputDirectory - optional override for TN3270 output directory
public record AssembleConfig(IoMode ioMode, Optional<String> kafkaBootstrap, String kafkaSegmentsTopic, String kafkaHttpPairsTopic, String kafkaTnPairsTopic, Path inputDirectory, Path outputDirectory, boolean httpEnabled, boolean tnEnabled, Optional<Path> httpOutputDirectory, Optional<Path> tnOutputDirectory) extends Record
Configuration for the assemble CLI pipeline.
Since:
RADAR 0.1-doc
